data.description: Welcome to 7107 Brookside Lane in the beautiful Northwood area!      Updated by the current owners, with today's must-have features to including "Alexa" enabled smart features, yet preserving the charm of the home's original character! First impressions begin with the over-sized lot (.69 acres) & the most inviting entryway!  Home features include: grand architectural design, 4000+ square feet, 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, 2 stories WITH a finished walk-out basement (fun area with multiple purposes!), 3 living areas (formal, family & basement), 2 dining areas to include an eat-in kitchen & formal dining room, recessed lighting, decorator paint/accent colors, vaulted ceilings, ceiling fans for energy efficiency, & beautiful lighting fixtures to name a few!  Gas cooking kitchen, w/quartz countertops, Blum soft close drawers, elongated cabinets w/molding finish at ceiling, sub-zero/built-in refrigerator, breakfast bar, wine/drink refrigerator, built-out bar area under stairs w/an additional sink & ice maker. The primary bedroom is on the main level. Work in the private office with custom built-in drawers and shelving. Enjoy outdoor living w/an in-ground pool & a POOL HOUSE (think office, spa, exercise gym, she-shed or man-cave!), mature trees, fenced yard & dog run!  The most recent updates & upgrades include: Alexa Enabled Smart Home w/automated lights, four zoned thermostats for energy efficiency, outdoor pergola, pool pump, custom iron front door, sliding doors in kitchen, French doors in living room, custom maple kitchen cabinets, kitchen countertops & appliances, sub-zero refrigerator, commercial grade Blue Star range, hardwood floors, staircase, bathroom upstairs w/luxury shower heads (rainfall & multiple), carpet in primary bedroom & entryway chandelier! Centrally located & near all major highways, this is one of San Antonio's beauties!
